🥰Coming soon Mixed Media Class #2 on Tuesday April 11th at Gateway Art Gallery from 5:15-7:15 with Laura Hunter-Null. 
🥰Below is “Coral Reef Diving”, a mixed media piece using watercolor, acrylics, gold leaf, paint writers, metallic acrylic, black and colored permanent pens and writers. 
🥰The cost is $35.00, pay, before the day of the class $30.00. We are closed on Sunday and Monday. 
🥰Bring any of your favorite brushes, roll of paper towel and masking tape. If you have any stiff card board pieces, 12x16 or larger bring it to work on. It’s your time to get away and have fun making art together.

Hi everyone!

I wasn’t able to attend John Larner fantastic en plain air oil paint class this Friday and Saturday, 10-12 each day. My “River” bug came down with strep throat so LaLa and River are spending good time together. While she’s watching some kids shows, I have been breaking out the oils paints here at home. 

The Gateway Art Gallery - Art League of North FL artist are presenting a tribute to Fathers, we will be displaying recently created artwork for the entire month of June. I was trying to think of something to bring that would embody the feelings of summer, outdoors, beauty, tranquility, a cool and restful place. A place my husband would love. So I decide to paint a spring. I though of the Ichetucknee river springs. We dearly love these springs, we visit and kayak this beautiful river several times each year. 

I am in the process of finishing this large oil painting that represents the head spring of the Ichetucknee river. Not quite finished, hope it dries enough to hang before June 1st. ☺️

Mixed Media Class 8/8/23, Laura Hunter-Null
Gateway Art Gallery - Art League of North FL

August Artist, Piet Mondrian b 1872- d 1944, will be featured. A Dutch Artist, who is regarded as one of the greatest artists of the 20th century. He is known for being one of the pioneers of 20th-century abstract art. 

We will be using Nuvo Dimensional; Crystal, Glitter, & Stone Drops, Golden Acrylic; Interference paints & Iridescent metallic paint, Liquid Pearl; Dimensional Pearlescent paint, and Silver & Gold leaf on Black Matt board, to create an abstract painting using simple geometric elements.

$35.00-Pay early $30.00

This class has been rescheduled for 8/22/23.
